data.description: Location, location, location! Welcome to the highly sought after neighborhood of Dana Pointe. A short walk leads directly to the private neighborhood dock and boat launch on the Choctawhatchee Bay. Sitting on over half an acre, this home has endless opportunities inside and out. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, vaulted ceilings, and a beautiful fireplace, this home will not disappoint. The open floor plan and sunroom boasting a wet bar and beverage fridge make this home perfect for entertaining! Don't miss your opportunity to view this fantastic home!
